**File:** `DockerEntityPolicy.kt`
All the specific name/image checks inside the `isRunningStatus` block are unreachable dead code because the function unconditionally returns `true` for any running container (the final `return true`). The intermediate checks add no value and create misleading specificity. Either remove the blanket `return true` (and let the specific conditions control the behavior), or remove the specific checks and document that ALL running containers are protected by design.
